{
  "stem": "4753.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And sometimes, they almost choked me, because my prediction, that how can I say things like that, and got angry at me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But somehow, I never gave up hope and faith.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And from there, I did go to, to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We stayed in tents, because in the buildings were not enough space.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The tent was just tied down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But between the tent and the ground were a big gap.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So the water from all the places were running in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So inside, the mud was exactly as big as outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We couldn't lay down, naturally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were sitting and supporting each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "By the way, that was in Auschwitz, too, in the B3, supporting each other with each other's back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You know, we were sitting back to each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And that's the way we kept each other up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And from Bergen-Belsen later, suddenly a lot of people disappeared.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We didn't know they were all cremated or, or shot, whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then finally, we came into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "There, we didn't spend too much time, because we were taken to other places to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And that's the way I came to Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "That was a beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I remember early morning, we were going in the dark to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And you could see the homes, houses, because it's just a silhouette.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And one wall clearly before my eyes, because that was some big building full of statues on the top.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And one wall with the statues was still standing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I don't know how come that didn't fell off of something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And in our-- in Braunschweig, I had the most happy moment in my life when I was cleaning the street with the group, naturally.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
